description: McpcPSCellProfile: Table storing configuration profiles for MPCP PS cells, including identification, area, and metadata.  dateTime: Timestamp of profile entry; Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell; CellId: Unique identifier for the cell; Id2: Redundant cell identifier; Id3:  Auxiliary identifier (likely unused); Id4:  Auxiliary identifier (likely indicating default profile); vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format; McpcPSCellProfile.mcpcPSCellProfileId: Profile ID; McpcPSCellProfile.userLabel: User-defined label; McpcPSCellProfile.reservedBy:  Indicates if the profile is reserved.
